des: I, RickyHSV, am a full time Professional foodie. With over 15 years in the restaurant industry all across the Rocket city and my passion to share my dining experiences with the world. Have created this flash briefing to keep you up to date on what’s new. What’s trending. Where I eat. And other food news and updates from my foodie adventures around town.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
